Content.title: meemalee
Content.name: meemalee
Content.bodyText:
Hooray! I'm so chuffed that you took my advice - did they seem confused when you went in? ("Who are these people? What do they want? Oh yes, we run a restaurant")

By the way, I went to Fressen (it's near my work) just to see how bad it was - the limp watercress still haunts me ...
